g><span style=\"font-size:14px\">spring.jackson.mapper</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">是否开启Jackson通用的特性.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">spring.jackson.parser</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">是否开启jackson的parser特性.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">spring.jackson.property-naming-strategy</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">指定PropertyNamingStrategy(CAMEL_CASE_TO_LOWER_CASE_WITH_UNDERSCORES)或者指定PropertyNamingStrategy子类的全限定类名.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">spring.jackson.serialization</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">是否开启jackson的序列化.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">spring.jackson.serialization-inclusion</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">指定序列化时属性的inclusion方式，具体查看JsonInclude.Include枚举.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">spring.jackson.time-zone</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">指定日期格式化时区，比如America/Los_Angeles或者GMT+10.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">PS.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">来源：<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/liaojie970/p/9396334.html\" target=\"_blank\">springboot之jackson的两种配置方式</a></span></p>\r\n','2021-01-13 04:41:17',42,7,0,NULL),(90,'MD5加密','Java代码：\n\npackage com;&nbsp;import java.math.BigInteger;import java.security.MessageDigest;&nbsp;/**&nbsp;* @author LeDao&nbsp;* @company&nbsp;* @create 2021-01-13 5:15&nbsp;*/public class Md5 &#123;&nbsp;    public static final String KEY_MD5 = &quot;MD5&quot;;&nbsp;    public static  String  getResult&#40;String inputStr&#41;    &#123;        System.out.println&#40;&quot;=======加密前的数据:&quot;+inputStr&#41;;        BigInteger bigInteger=null;&nbsp;        try &#123;            MessageDigest md = MessageDigest.getInstance&#40;KEY_MD5&#41;;            byte&#91;&#93; i